  "texts": [
    "19 Despite the MBI receiving criticism for discounting burnout in informal work environments, it is an appropriate choice for assessing burnout in a healthcare workplace and was therefore used in this study.",
    "Standard MBI is a 22-item burnout assessment tool widely adopted by healthcare workers.",
    "It measures three dimensions: nine measure emotional exhaustion (EE), five evaluate depersonalisation (DP) and eight measure personal accomplishment (PA).",
    "Individuals scoring highly on EE and DP and scoring low on PA were associated with a mindfulness courses, mentorship programmes, Enhanced Stress Resilience Training (ESRT) and Self-Compassion for Healthcare Communities (SCHC) training.",
    "Dedicated faculty and wellness opportunities produced lower burnout rates (p=0.02)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "19 Despite the MBI receiving criticism for discounting burnout in informal work environments, it is an appropriate choice for assessing burnout in a healthcare workplace and was therefore used in this study."
  ]
}